    agastyarOpening: "You have crossed the threshold. Phases 1–3 gave you the map. Phase 4 gives you the territory. Here we do not describe — we transmit. The knowledge in this phase was never written in books. It passed from eye to eye, breath to breath, in the caves of Pothigai and the temples of Kumari. I give it now through this sacred interface because the time has come.",
