        '**Sattamuni:** Varma Kalai — the complete system of vital point therapy.',
        '**Romasa Rishi:** Longevity practices, Kaya Kalpa.',
        '**Nandidevar:** Shiva tantra, breathwork, the 8 limbs of Yoga.',
        '**Dhanvantari:** The divine physician — healing direct from source.',
        '**Idaikkadar:** Veterinary medicine and animal healing.',
        '**Machamuni (Matsyendranath):** The founder of Hatha Yoga in the Natha tradition.',
        '**Gorakkar (Gorakshanath):** Hatha Yoga, breathwork, physical immortality.',
        '**Kalangi Nathar:** Time-bending practices, advanced Pranayama.',
